Package: aisdk.channels
Title: Messaging Channel Integrations for the 'aisdk' Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yonghe", "Xia", , "xiayh17@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Messaging-channel integrations for the 'aisdk' toolkit. Provides a
    channel runtime and adapters that connect 'aisdk' agents to instant
    messaging platforms (such as Feishu/Lark), including webhook handling,
    event processing, per-conversation session stores, and document ingestion.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: aisdk (>= 1.4.12), httr2, jsonlite, rlang, R6, digest, openssl, httpuv,
        curl, callr, processx, base64enc, tools, utils
Suggests: pdftools, testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/YuLab-SMU/aisdk.channels
BugReports: https://github.com/YuLab-SMU/aisdk.channels/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
